{"tid":2354927,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"起初他們（德國納粹黨）追殺共產主義者， 因為我不是共產主義者，我不說話；","createTime":"2021-01-06T00:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:54:02.000Z","uid":230104,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72e971ffb31a28ae1f1287f050a94db5fef26b92","tid":2354927,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"馬丁．尼莫拉（Martin Niemoller 1892-1984），是二次大戰前德國的宗教領袖，因為對希特勒的猶太政策和對德國教會的控制，後來被希特勒親自下令送進集中營。<br />\n<br />\n二次世界大戰以後，德國牧師馬丁．尼莫拉（Martin Niemoller 1892-1984）為了讓世人記住納粹屠殺猶太人這一血腥恥辱，在波士頓樹起了一塊紀念碑，碑上銘刻這樣一段話：<br />\n<br />\n起初他們（德國納粹黨）追殺共產主義者，<br />\n因為我不是共產主義者，我不說話；<br />\n<br />\n接著他們追殺猶太人，<br />\n因為我不是猶太人，我不說話；<br />\n<br />\n後來他們追殺工會成員，<br />\n因為我不是工會成員，我繼續不說話；<br />\n<br />\n此後他們追殺天主教徒，<br />\n因為我不是天主教徒，我還是不說話；<br />\n<br />\n最後，他們奔向我來，<br />\n再也沒有人站起來為我說話了。"},{"pid":"552c060b109caaa3580f40f7e3b440e27a3333f0","tid":2354927,"uid":80679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:17:12.000Z","msg":"華人心態驚槍打出頭鳥同自掃門前雪<br />\n最岩做韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ee6e0d97b8f4f814794c4c6fc9982116fb1caa","tid":2354927,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:24:16.000Z","msg":"我移民咪得囉"},{"pid":"d9c98281dae5c15a13aaf572ac63589eb3e1a727","tid":2354927,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf0208de7e30fc2be94b44c7ca90f87c67e4fb1","tid":2354927,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"退無可退"},{"pid":"9fd0f143b797beb24039f36f42f3b36eed036c59","tid":2354927,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee4932794d2e580c